{"tid":1333913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話自己好攰嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-20T02:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T02:43:21.000Z","uid":230798,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"090d42a2df163855d283c65008608437e8cb6eb2","tid":1333913,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:21:23.000Z","msg":"我理得你攰唔攰，721都同我出黎唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋建制今日吹囇雞咁叫人出黎，我哋自己內部仲俾人玩緊分化，啲垃圾膠post都俾人推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解一個721嘅文宣、戰術post都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解一個721嘅文宣、戰術post都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解一個721嘅文宣、戰術post都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有有邊個唔攰，我自己都好攰，但係睇住班狗咁樣打人，個政府又咁垃圾，幾攰都要出嚟行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次班狗份不反對通知書淨係去到灣仔，遊行路線縮短咗，唔代表我哋會少人左，上次隊尾去到北角，我要今次隊尾去到太古城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都係果句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n721你地搞唔掂政府，我話既！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333335</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[721裝備攻略] 只需12蚊即可施展打狗捧法！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333601